quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  16,88,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e Alla, Й“e faddii woЙ—Й“e goo e laawol Alla ngol, Men Й“eydiranii Й“e lepte Й—e Й“e hanndi Й—en, e hoore lepte goo, sabu ko bonni kon Й“e majjini woЙ—Й“e goo."
  16,89,"Janto kadi an NulaaЙ—o, Гұalnde Men immintinoyta e kala mofte, NulaaЙ—o seeditoytooЙ—o e hoore maЙ“Й“e e ko Й“e wonunoo e keeferaaku maa gomЙ—inal, NulaaЙ—o jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, wowloowo haala maЙ“Й“e. Men adda maa an NulaaЙ—o, ko seeditoo e mofte Й—en fow. Men jippinii e maaЙ—a Alqur'aana, fii yo nde Й“anngin kala ko hatonjini e Й“anngineede, immorde e halal e haram, mbarjaari e lepte, ekn. Men jippiniri nde ko fewna yimЙ“e Й“en e goonga, e yurmeende kala gomЙ—inoowo nden o gollira nde, e welo-welo gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla Й“en e kon ko Й“e habbitii e neema ГұiiЙ“oowo."
  16,90,"Tabitii Alla yamirii jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en nunЙ—al, nde tottata haqqeeji Alla Й—in e haqqeeji jeyaaЙ“e Й“en, hara kadi goЙ—Й—o Й“urnaaka e hoore goЙ—Й—o goo ka Гұaawoore si wanaa hara ko no jojjiri. Himo yamira moЖҙЖҙingol, nde jeyaaЙ—o on waЙ—irta ko fawaaki mo kon -wano wintagol- yarlitaare e yaafanagol too- ГұuЙ—o. Himo yamira kadi moЖҙЖҙoragol e joomiraЙ“e Й“adondiral Й“en ko Й“e hatonjinta e mun ko. E senngo goo, Himo haЙ—a kala ko kaani, wano konngol pankare maa kuuЙ—e jeeno. Himo haЙ—a kadi gaay e tooГұe, e townitagol e yimЙ“e Й“en. Himo waajora on ko O yamiri on kon e ko O haЙ—i on e mun kon e Й—ee Aayeeje, belajo'o, on taskoto waajitoron."
  16,91,"Hunnee kala ahadi ndi ahoduЙ—on e Alla maa ndi ahoduЙ—on e yimЙ“e Й“en, wata on firtu goondooje mon Й—en Й“aawo Й—e tentinireede woondirgol Alla, gomЙ—ii on waЙ—ii Alla seeditaniiЙ—o on e hunngol ko woonduЙ—on kon. Pellet, Alla ko annduЙ—o ko gollo- ton: huunde e mun suuЙ—aaki Mo, O yoЙ“itoyay on Й—um."
  16,92,"Wata on wonir e firtugol ahadiiji Й—in, njofooЙ“e faaЙ—uЙ“e haqqille, wano on debbo komoojo, tampunooЙ—o e harlugol hottollo makko kon: nde o gaynunoo harlude kon, o firti ko fow kadi o artiri no wa'unoo. O tampini hoore meere. Awa onon kadi, hiЙ—on jogitora goondooje mon Й—en janfondiro hak- kunde mon, fii yo mofte mon Й—en Й“uri mofte ayЙ“e mon Й“en doole e Й—uuЙ—ere. Anndee Alla no jarribo- ra on huuЙ“nugol ahadiiji Й—in, anndugol si on laati-nay kaa on firtay Й—i? Ma Alla Й“annginanoy on Г‘alnde Darngal, kon ko luutondiraynoЙ—on e mun aduna, O sennda hakkunde goonguЙ—o e meerente, goongiyanke e fenoowo."
  16,93,"Sinno Alla muuyuno, O waЙ—ayno on mofte goote, nanondirayЙ—e e goonga. Ko woni tun, Himomajji- nira nunЙ—al Makko ngal huccinirgol on Mo O muuyi e gooonga e hunnugol ahadi, O fewnira Й“ural mak- ko ngal on Mo O muuyi. Ma on lannditoye Г‘alnde Darngal, e kon ko luutondiraynoЙ—on e mun aduna."